                Planning



              Approving the IT and information or data component of all departmental strategies, plans, initiatives, projects, procurements and spending authority requests;
              Producing the departmental IT expenditure report and ongoing Application Portfolio Management update reports; and
              Ensuring that departmental IT investments, service development and improvement initiatives are informed by and integrated into departmental business planning;







